# Tailwind v4 Design System Tokens

Use Tailwind v4 `@theme` tokens defined in [src/app/globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css). Prefer semantic utilities over arbitrary values.

## Typography

- Fonts: `font-geist`
- Sizes: `text-h1`, `text-h2`, `text-h3`, `text-body`, `text-body2`
- Leading: prefer `leading-none` per Figma

## Colors

- Primary: `bg-primary-{blue|red|green|yellow|purple|white|black|dark-gray}`
- Secondary (panels): `bg-secondary-{blue|red|green|yellow|purple|grey}`
- Text examples: `text-primary-black`, `text-primary-dark-gray`

## Components

- CTA button: `rounded-cta shadow-cta bg-primary-white text-primary-black`

## Principles

- Do NOT use hex values in classes when a token exists
- New tokens should be added to [globals.css](mdc:src/app/globals.css) under `@theme` with Tailwind namespaces: `--color-*`, `--text-*`, `--font-*`, `--radius-*`, `--shadow-*`
